# Browser work

Read the **browser-validation** skill first. Two tiers — never mix them:

| Tier | Package / tool | Use for |
| ---- | -------------- | ------- |
| **Verify** | `@repo/browser-tools`, `chrome-devtools` MCP | DOM assertions, selector checks — no artifacts |
| **Capture** | `@repo/browser-capture`, `devtools-capture` MCP | HAR, traces, Web Vitals, console — produces artifacts |

- Routine DOM/text checks: `pnpm browser:validate` or `chrome-devtools` MCP — **not** `record_trace`.
- CI smoke (verify): `.github/workflows/verify-browser-smoke.yml`
- CI artifacts (capture): `.github/workflows/capture-devtools.yml`

App URL port is declared as `devPort` in each app's `package.json` (5173 / 8080 / 8000). Always pass `--url` explicitly in examples and CI.

Full decision tree: [`docs/browser-validation.md`](../../docs/browser-validation.md)
